<title>无标题文档</title>
<style>

.box1{ width:70%;height:40px; background-color:#0F9;position:absolute; }
.box2{ width:80%; height:30px; background-color:#C39;position:fixed;}
.content{ width:90%; height:70px; background-color:#03F;}
.wrap{width:99%;height:210px; background-color:#666;}
